    "This will ensure that the integration of LMFMs in educational settings is done responsibly, ethically, and effectively, contributing to a future where technology enhances the educational experience.Critical assessment and cross-referencing: Embracing a critical mindset entails consistently comparing LMFM-generated outputs with established resources, upholding the integrity of scholarly claims.Diversified LMFM training data and bias mitigation: Advocating for diversified training data and employing bias detection and mitigation techniques helps in fostering fairer and more inclusive research outcomes."
